description: This simple coffee and walnut cake makes a delicious tea time treat.
name: Coffee & Walnut Cake Recipe | Woolworths

recipeInstructions.text: Whisk the mascarpone, icing sugar and vanilla in a large bowl. Smooth the icing on top of the cake, decorate with extra walnuts if desired, slice and serve.
